"     Reprinted by permission from Macmillan Publishers Ltd: Leukemia, Comenzo RL, Reece D, Palladini G, Consensus guidelines for the conduct and reporting of clinical trials in systemic light-chain amyloidosis, advance online publication, 15 May 2012 (DOI: 10.1038/leu.2012.100). Copyright &copy; 2012.",
